            crit: "Product-contact surface finish commonly Ra ≤ 0.5 µm; dead legs eliminated/minimized per the L/D rule; materials (e.g. SS316L) with traceable certificates. Confirm the exact Ra and acceptance against the project design basis and BPE edition.",
