    "desc": "Qualification of pharmaceutical water generation, storage, and distribution (PW and WFI). The chemical limits are compendial (USP <645> conductivity, <643> TOC; WFI adds endotoxin/microbial), but which grade and points-of-use apply is process-driven. PQ is the classic three-phase sampling program over ~12 months.",
    "icon": "<svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#58e6a8\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M12 3c4 5 6 8 6 11a6 6 0 0 1-12 0c0-3 2-6 6-11z\"/></svg>",
