            "id": "USP <1231> three-phase PQ",
            "issuer": "USP / ISPE Baseline Guide",
            "covers": "Phase 3 long-term monitoring across seasonal variation.",
            "crit": "Reduced routine sampling over ~12 months demonstrates the system stays in spec across seasons; sets the routine monitoring program.",
